## 🔄 Auto-evolution protocol

| Moment | Command |
|---|---|
| When correcting an error | `ouroboros learn <category> "<lesson>" "<trigger>"` |
| When a pattern repeats 2+ times | `ouroboros skill <name> "<description>"` |
| At the start of each session | `ouroboros session-start` |
| Before declaring a task complete | `ouroboros self-check` |
| At the end of each session | `ouroboros session-end "<summary>"` |

**Valid categories:** `seguridad` · `interfaz` · `funcionalidad` · `operatividad` · `arquitectura` · `performance` · `testing` · `datos` · `auth` · `docker`

